        "Resolving CNI networking failures (e.g., Cilium/Calico) and CoreDNS bottlenecks is critical for maintaining stable microservice communication.",
        "Misconfigured resource requests and limits lead to silent OOMKills, noisy neighbors, and runaway cloud infrastructure costs."
      ]
